<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Portfolio — Mechanical Design Engineer</title>
<style>
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  :root{--navy:#1a2332;--accent:#2563eb;--light:#f8f9fa;--muted:#6b7280;--border:#e5e7eb;--white:#ffffff}
  body{font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;color:#1f2937;background:#fff;line-height:1.6}
  a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
  nav{position:sticky;top:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 2rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;height:60px;z-index:100}
  .nav-logo{font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;color:var(--navy)}
  .nav-links{display:flex;gap:2rem;list-style:none}
  .nav-links a{font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--muted);transition:color .2s}
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--navy)}
  section{padding:5rem 2rem;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto}
  .hero{padding:6rem 2rem 5rem;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto}
  .hero-tag{display:inline-block;background:#eff6ff;color:var(--accent);font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:500;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;letter-spacing:.04em}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem);font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .hero p{font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:560px;margin-bottom:2rem}
  .hero-btns{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;padding:10px 24px;border-radius:6px;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:500;transition:opacity .2s}
  .btn-primary:hover{opacity:.85;color:#fff}
  .btn-outline{border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--navy);padding:10px 24px;border-radius:6px;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:500;transition:background .2s}
  .btn-outline:hover{background:var(--light)}
  .divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:0}
  h2{font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .section-sub{color:var(--muted);font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem}
  .about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:start}
  .about-text p{color:#374151;margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:0.97rem}
  .about-stats{display:grid;gap:1rem}
  .stat-card{background:var(--light);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.25rem}
  .stat-num{font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy)}
  .stat-label{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
  .projects-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:1.5rem}
  .project-card{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow .2s}
  .project-card:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
  .project-img{height:160px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:2.5rem;background:var(--light)}
  .project-body{padding:1.25rem}
  .project-tag{display:inline-block;background:#eff6ff;color:var(--accent);font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:500;padding:2px 10px;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:.6rem}
  .project-body h3{font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.4rem}
  .project-body p{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
  .skills-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:1.5rem}
  .skill-group h3{font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .skill-list{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem}
  .skill-pill{background:var(--light);border:1px solid var(--border);color:#374151;font-size:0.82rem;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px}
  .contact-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem}
  .contact-text p{color:#374151;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .contact-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.75rem}
  .contact-link{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#374151}
  .contact-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--light);border:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;flex-shrink:0}
  .contact-form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.75rem}
  .contact-form input,.contact-form textarea{padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;font-size:0.9rem;font-family:inherit;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;background:#fff;color:#1f2937}
  .contact-form input:focus,.contact-form textarea:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
  .contact-form textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:110px}
  .contact-form button{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;padding:11px;border:none;border-radius:6px;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:opacity .2s}
  .contact-form button:hover{opacity:.85}
  footer{text-align:center;padding:2rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border);font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted)}
  @media(max-width:640px){
    .about-grid,.contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    nav{padding:0 1rem}
    section,.hero{padding:3rem 1.2rem}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <span class="nav-logo">Jane Smith</span>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- Hero -->
<div class="hero">
  <span class="hero-tag">Mechanical Design Engineer</span>
  <h1>Designing precision<br/>engineering solutions</h1>
  <p>Experienced in CAD design, product development, and manufacturing — turning complex problems into elegant, manufacturable parts.</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="#projects" class="btn-primary">View my work</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-outline">Get in touch</a>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="divider"/>

<!-- About -->
<section id="about">
  <h2>About me</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Engineer, problem-solver, and lifelong tinkerer.</p>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>I'm a mechanical design engineer with a passion for creating efficient, reliable, and manufacturable designs. My work spans product development cycles from concept to production, with a strong focus on DFM and tolerance analysis.</p>
      <p>I thrive in collaborative environments and enjoy working closely with manufacturing, testing, and cross-functional teams to bring ideas to life.</p>
      <p>When I'm not in CAD, you'll find me 3D printing side projects and exploring new fabrication techniques.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-stats">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-num">6+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Years of experience</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-num">20+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Projects delivered</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-num">3</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Industries served</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider"/>

<!-- Projects -->
<section id="projects">
  <h2>Projects</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">A selection of engineering work across industries and scales.</p>
  <div class="projects-grid">
    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-img">⚙️</div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <span class="project-tag">Aerospace</span>
        <h3>Bracket assembly redesign</h3>
        <p>Redesigned a structural bracket assembly reducing part count by 40% while maintaining FEA-validated load requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-img">🔩</div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <span class="project-tag">Consumer products</span>
        <h3>Ergonomic handle mechanism</h3>
        <p>Developed a spring-loaded locking handle with tool-free assembly, improving user experience and reducing production cost.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-img">🏭</div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <span class="project-tag">Industrial</span>
        <h3>Conveyor jig tooling</h3>
        <p>Designed custom fixturing and jig tooling for a high-volume assembly line, cutting cycle time by 25%.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-img">🌊</div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <span class="project-tag">Fluid systems</span>
        <h3>Hydraulic manifold block</h3>
        <p>Created a compact manifold block integrating 6 solenoid valve circuits, replacing a complex tube assembly with a single machined component.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-img">🚗</div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <span class="project-tag">Automotive</span>
        <h3>Heat shield enclosure</h3>
        <p>Designed a stamped sheet metal heat shield enclosure with integrated noise dampening to meet OEM thermal and acoustic specs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-img">🔬</div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <span class="project-tag">Medical devices</span>
        <h3>Instrument housing</h3>
        <p>Developed an IP67-rated enclosure for a handheld diagnostic instrument, designed for injection moulding and sterilisation compliance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider"/>

